data.description: Come home to this like new, 5 bedroom, 4 1/2 bath home in the sought after Grandview Estates. This master on main, 3 side brick home sits on a 1.34 acre level lot. With a 3 car garage and unfinished basement this home has all the room and potential you need to make it your own. Walk in the front door to a 2 story foyer, coffered ceilings throughout and perfectly cared for wood floors. This open concept floor plan is perfect for entertaining. The kitchen has a large island, white/cream cabinets, stone countertops, and a huge walk in pantry and that opens up to a cozy keeping room complete with a stacked stone fireplace and beamed ceiling. Also open to the kitchen is a breakfast area that overlooks the backyard. This home has a covered front porch ready for your rocking chairs but also a 2 level covered back porch for more private relaxing and entertaining. The back porch has a vaulted, bead board ceiling and stairs down to the concrete patio below. This home has been meticulously maintained and will not disappoint. Just minutes from Lake Lanier and 985 the location is hard to beat.
